OL,6,FA series of changes to disability
OL,7,Fbenefits were announced in the
OL,8,FChancellor's Spring Budget on
OL,9,FWednesday, amounting to what Jeremy
OL,10,FHunt called the "biggest change to our
OL,11,Fwelfare system in a decade".
OL,13,FThe reforms included the scrapping of
OL,14,Fthe work capability assessment (WCA) to
OL,15,Fdetermine eligibility for sickness
OL,16,Fbenefits, a move which was welcomed by
OL,17,Fcampaigners.
OL,19,FMr Hunt also announced a new employment
OL,20,Fscheme for disabled people called
OL,21,FUniversal Support.
